search_results.title: Hank & Tank WWE | News, Rumors & Biography
search_results.snippet: Hank & Tank is a professional tag team in WWE NXT comprising Hank Walker and Tank Ledger. Hank Walker was born on June 11, 1998, in Hampstead, North Carolina.
